Class EditRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentCallbacks, ComponentCallbacks2, KeyEvent.Callback, LayoutInflater.Factory, LayoutInflater.Factory2, View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, Window.Callback, DeleteDialogFragment.DeleteDialogListener

    public class EditRule
extends Activity
implements DeleteDialogFragment.DeleteDialogListener
    The EditRule class is the main Activity for rule creation This Activity is used for creating, editing, and viewing rules The Rule creation constantly comes back to this screen to show the user the progress on the rule creation The rCauses, rCause boolean logic, rEffects, Rule Name, and Rule Active Status are all displayed on this Activity
    Author:
    CEandroid SMU
